CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Soluna is on a mission to make renewable energy a global superpower using computing as a catalyst. The company designs, develops, and operates digital infrastructure that transforms surplus renewable energy into global computing resources. Soluna's pioneering data centers are strategically co-located with wind, solar, or hydroelectric power plants to support high-performance computing applications including Bitcoin Mining, Generative AI, and other compute-intensive applications. Soluna''s proprietary software MaestroOS(TM) helps energize a greener grid while delivering cost-effective and sustainable computing solutions, and superior returns.
